description: Apple Inc. is an American multinational technology company headquartered in Cupertino, California, that designs, develops, and sells consumer electronics, computer software, and online services.
Microsoft Corporation is an American multinational technology corporation that produces computer software, consumer electronics, personal computers, and related services.
Alphabet Inc. is an American multinational conglomerate headquartered in Mountain View, California. It is the parent company of Google and several other businesses.
